Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Please look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I got it, you hear? I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look at it! I will, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh so much, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Me need to practice more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this tot your little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch me try it out once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru, what's that girl's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know, first met her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She - my lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru! Dinner, dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl I first met sent my heart pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I already gave an oath to marry Iyona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner, dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Wh... What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were too absorbed in thought, \NI brought bicycle to life with Magic-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And told him to dru-ru-rive at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna get ya there! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! You can't be serious, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:05.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HBAB1AE&\3c&H5B641F&}Zakenja Neyo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I introduce to everyone our new transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja Neyo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, it's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I hope you all make good friends with Zakenja-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Zakenja-san? {actually "now, it's your turn to say something"}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.62,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that conclude your introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you can take your seat at the furthermost row.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had no time to receive your textbook today, \Nso please ask your neighbor to let you see theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I bought and brought my own kendama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we mistake her for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the first! {guess, kinda like moeru yo but idk who's burning and why}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No running in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, in the test from the other day, \Nwhy did you cross this answer? {could be w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Her air is completely different somehow, Taru. {a certain air; presence; special aura; something (about someone)}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zakenja-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you used to live before moving here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Iyona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, that was kinda to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking it on herself to break the ice \Nwith a new transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how caring you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee... Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When asking others about something, \Nyou first introduce yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kawai Iyona.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And this here is Ijigawa Rui-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any questions, feel free to ask me. {/If you want to know something, ask me anytime.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are just incorrigible. {no clue what she "can't help"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Elementary school students these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know no manners, {rude; impolite; mannerless; snotty}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,no nothing. {unsure she means this}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be doing that! \NElementary school students don't smoke cigars!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I know, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to open the window or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja-san, smoking is very bad for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, you're obnoxious. You don't go around \Ntelling people this and that pastime is wrong! {to say this and that (about); to say (critical) things; to criticize; to be critical (about); to find fault (with); to complain; to raise objections (to); to meddle (in); to interfere (in)}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I still think... That one thing... {no clue what she means}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get to preach others \Njust 'cause you have a pretty little face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda game do you think you're playing here, \Nyou stuck-up arrogant whore?! Huh? {no clue what she means: お高くとまってえらそーに何様のつもり!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're not actually that kind of girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw your true face, when you smiled yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I sincerely hope \Nto see that kind smile of yours once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! She heeded to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So corny! {kusai - no clue, already used stinker in prev. ep}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I'm impressed that you can say such corny lines \Nout loud without even feeling slightly embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl with a potty mouth is as far from cute as it can get. {to say nasty things (about); to use abusive language}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Harako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this dino-mugged grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit... You even dare to call me a dino-mugged Grandpa?! {half-guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tolerate anyone saying such things, \Nnot even a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've won that {fight }already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've almost done it! \NBut I'm also the World Junior Endurance... {unsure, was 無差別 in manga, but here sounds more like 耐久性 but still doesn't make sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wide Swing Brain Stem Wrecking Ball Hit! {actually last part is kinda "fall of the rock"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...{nc}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All bark and no bite, as always. {all bark and no bite; unable to live up to one's claims}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! Pathetic poser. {false impression; deceptive appearance; mere show}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever else has a problem with me, step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to deal with you anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one hell of a transferred girl we got...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Harako-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you giving me that look? \NGot a problem with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me, Iyona-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a problem with you. \NI just think violence is unacceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,For a champion of every world tournament {for the best of the best }\Nin any kind of sports...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I wrong for shutting up a guy \Ntrying to pick a fight with me? {tlc, doesn't make much sense to me the exact line from manga is いんねんふっかけてくるやつをしめてどこがわるいのさ? } {17:23: I'm hearing 因縁ふっかけてくるやつをしめてどこが悪いのさ\NThe first part of the line is a combination of two different elements. Not sure why they did that.\Nhttps://jisho.org/word/%E5%90%B9%E3%81%A3%E6%8E%9B%E3%81%91%E3%82%8B \N https://jisho.org/word/%E5%9B%A0%E7%B8%81%E3%82%92%E3%81%A4%E3%81%91%E3%82%8B \N The scene shows Iyona having a problem with the way the transfer student took care of Harako.\Nどこが悪いのさ is basically the transfer student saying "How am I in the wrong/What's wrong with that?"\N\NI think what you have now is fine tbh.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you could easily get along \Nwithout resorting to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to preach again? \NThat's some guts you got, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If it came to this, we gotta save Iyona-chan with magic! \NKnock out the other girl! {/beat/defeat/attack/do away with}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock out? But me love both Iyona and the other girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Got nothing better to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zakenja-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If a bunch of elementary graders look down on me\Nas soon as I transfer, I ain't gonna stand for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Aren't you an elementary grader yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Violence only leaves behind more hatred and deep scars. \NIt's a line I've read in some book.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to you \Nat your previous school. But in our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just cut the crap already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already won this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? {\i1}You{\i0} won?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,With this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win, you apologize to everyone in class there and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Without violence, we'll hold a duel strictly with kendama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Kendama duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan to beat {\i1}me{\i0} in kendama mastery?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let me down, Kendama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trust me to deal with it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Honmaru-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you babbling about there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving me no choice but to attack first.{unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru will be fine! Duel, duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... It's my turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, Honmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of technique is this? \NIt's almost like the ball is moving on its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you could almost say it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... But please, try to move just a bit slower! {half guess, kinda hear mo ososhiki you ni ugokashite}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about how much I can do, \Nonly engaging a fraction of my true ability! {unsure}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's enough playing. \NTime for a grand finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Any elementary grader is about ten years too young \Nto even try to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you understand you're an elementary grader yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought this upon yourself \Nby being unable to keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At least Honmaru-kun was trying to push his limits! {no clue how "doing his best" is a reason not to laugh}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Iyona-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?! He lost and that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You whore, still trying to talk back to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H59A3BD&\3c&H010416&\4c&H06612D&\bord0.9\shad4\fs30}Right on the mark! {unsure} {大当り}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Taru! Why'd you have to hit Iyona-chan too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to know a person so kind and caring as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one most wonderful here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh-heh-heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.73,0:22:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. This - Sabro. {友太刀}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The two you strike with it become best bros.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:07.17,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,600)\c&HB8BBCA&\bord0\fs40\blur0.8} Sabro {友太刀}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! You've really outdone yourself, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At one point, I thought the situation wasn't salvagable, \Nbut with this, peace returned to our class!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace, peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, Taru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do after the magic wears off in ten minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just strike them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And in ten minutes more?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Strike again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use! We haven't resolved anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, this is a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The "class needs" fund has disappeared! {教材費 is technically "teaching material fees" but it's evidently this fund they all chip in to buy things the class needs, I'm not sure what to call it in english}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's join the search with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Neyo! Start searching too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Neyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Neyo, let's look for it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.61,0:23:03.84,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,0)} Episode 41 \NDishonest Neyo! {素直じゃねえよ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Dishonest Neyo! {素直じゃねえよ!}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really love Neyo.
